# Documentation files (local reference only)
# Ignore specific documentation .md files (not README.md files)
# Using explicit patterns to avoid negation pattern issues
*.md
# Explicitly un-ignore README.md files using reliable patterns
# Root level README.md
!README.md
# README.md in any subdirectory (using explicit wildcard pattern)
!/*/README.md
!/*/*/README.md
!/*/*/*/README.md
!/*/*/*/*/README.md
!/*/*/*/*/*/README.md

